For this project Dataset has been provided by Coding Invaders LMS platform, then it connected to the Power Bi Desktop. 
Using power query data has been transformed and performed required data cleaning steps and data model has been generated for data analysis.


ðŸ‘‰Key Insights -

ðŸŒŸ A total of 334 shows have been released in each genre.

ðŸŒŸ Between 2008 and 2021, there were more movies released than TV shows, accounting for 69.12% of the total.

ðŸŒŸ The Netflix associate is interested in understanding show ratings, and out of a total of 1836 rated shows, all were classified as "TV-MA" (meaning only suitable for a mature audience).

ðŸŒŸ The Netflix associate wants to know the number of shows released each month, categorized by type (movie or TV show). In January and December, over 500 movies were released, which is higher than any other month.
